<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1"&gt;12S1 Sagāthāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/4"&gt;4 Mārasaṃyutta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/4/4.1"&gt;4.1 Paṭhamavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;4.1.9 Paṭhamaāyusutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Mārasaṃyutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Paṭhamavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Paṭhamaāyusutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_808"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;145.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;808&lt;/span&gt;Evaṃ me sutaṃ—  ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi—  “bhikkhavo”ti. “Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. Bhagavā etadavoca—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_809"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;809&lt;/span&gt;“Appamidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussānaṃ āyu. Gamanīyo samparāyo, kattabbaṃ kusalaṃ, caritabbaṃ brahmacariyaṃ. Natthi jātassa amaraṇaṃ. Yo, bhikkhave, ciraṃ jīvati, so vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo”ti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_810"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;810&lt;/span&gt;Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_811"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;811&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Dīghamāyu manussānaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;na naṃ hīḷe suporiso;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Careyya khīramattova,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;natthi maccussa āgamo”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_812"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;812&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Appamāyu manussānaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;hīḷeyya naṃ suporiso;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Careyyādittasīsova,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;natthi maccussa nāgamo”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_813"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;813&lt;/span&gt;Atha kho māro…pe…  tatthevantaradhāyīti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="273758" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 4.1.8 Nandatisutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="272701" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="273760" title="Go to next page"&gt;4.1.10 Dutiyaāyusutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
